episodes.title: Born Into Captivity, Insolation and control: 30 years in a cult
episodes.description:
🍀 I could rename this interview with Katy Morgan-Davies as 'the interview with one of the nicest person I have ever met'

We've made an effort to steer clear of repeating questions Katy has already answered in previous interviews. I hope you'll be able to follow along, even without prior knowledge of the cult.

2:29 Sequence II - The Interview
